*   ## **_Young Bucks and Death Riders def. Brodido and the Opps_**
    

The Young Bucks finally have money again!!!! They win $500k.

Matt Jackson rolls Bandido up while Nick holds the feet on the ropes.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/7f9150ec-ea7e-4861-b1df-ea7ef1e925e8/16193.jpg)

*   ## **Daniel Garcia has joined the Death Riders!!!**
    

Darby Allin runs out to stop the Death Riders from beating down the Opps. But a hooded man attacks Darby.

It's Daniel Garcia. He curbstomps Darby. Misses the chair then Curbstomps Darby directly into th chair on the second go.

Daniel Garcia has turned his back on AEW.